{"declarations":[{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/BVDecide/Normalize/EmbeddedConstraint.html#Lean.Meta.Tactic.BVDecide.Normalize.embeddedConstraintPass\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">BVDecide</span>.<span class=\"name\">Normalize</span>.<span class=\"name\">embeddedConstraintPass</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/BVDecide/Normalize/Basic.html#Lean.Meta.Tactic.BVDecide.Normalize.Pass\">Pass</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Substitute embedded constraints. That is look for hypotheses of the form `h : x = true` and use\nthem to substitute occurrences of `x` within other hypotheses. Additionally this drops all\nredundant top level hypotheses.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/BVDecide/Normalize/EmbeddedConstraint.html#Lean.Meta.Tactic.BVDecide.Normalize.embeddedConstraintPass","kind":"def","line":20,"name":"Lean.Meta.Tactic.BVDecide.Normalize.embeddedConstraintPass","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/BVDecide/Normalize/EmbeddedConstraint.lean#L20-L63"}}],"imports":["Lean.Meta.Tactic.BVDecide.Normalize.Basic","Std.Tactic.BVDecide.Normalize.Bool"],"instances":[],"name":"Lean.Meta.Tactic.BVDecide.Normalize.EmbeddedConstraint"}